getInstance

public static AndroidRadioDataProvider.RadioData getInstance(TelephonyManager telephonyManager,
                                                             CellLocation cellLocation,
                                                             int signalStrength,
                                                             ServiceState serviceState)
Constructs radioData object from the given telephony data.

Parameters:
telephonyManager - contains the TelephonyManager instance.
cellLocation - contains information about the current GSM cell.
signalStrength - is the strength of the network signal.
serviceState - contains information about the network service.
Returns:
a new RadioData object populated with the currently available network information or null if there isn't enough information.
